Package: ProMinerCore
Type: Package
Title: Probability calculations for three-part mineral resource assessments
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-06-01
Authors@R: c( person("Karl", "Ellefsen", email = "ellefsen@usgs.gov",
            role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Jeffery", "Phillips", email = "dsmith@usgs.gov",
            role = c("aut")))
Description: ProMinerCore is a software package that carries out
    the probability calculations for three-part
    mineral resource assessments. This package provide the core (essential)
    R functions to perform those calculations but does not provide a
    graphical user interface.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.02)
License: CC0
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    mvtnorm,
    ks,
    misc3d,
    rgl,
    ggplot2
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1

